io.github.goodees.ese.immutables

Interface ImmutableEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Event

    public interface ImmutableEvent
extends Event
    Base class for entity events using Immutables library. When an entity wants to use this approach for event serialization, it shall define its base class of events, that extends ImmutableEvent.

    All events for an entity need to be defined in same package!

    Event should implement this class. The package they reside in must have annotation ImmutablesSupport in their package-info.java
